Aragorn, Arwen, Legolas and Frodo tries to overtake the opposition in boats given to them by the elves in the Valley of the Silverlode.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Starting<br>
